  "wikitext": "{{Exclusivity|Shipwrecked|Hamlet}}\n{{Item Infobox\n|description = Bamboo is so versatile!\n|ingredient1 = Bamboo\n|multiplier1 = 3 {{SW|24}}\n|tab = Refine\n|tier = 1\n|stack = 20\n|spawnCode=\"fabric\"\n|burnTime = [[File:Light_Sources_Filter.png|32px|link=Fuel#Fire Fuel]] 45 sec\n|soldBy = {{Pic|32|Pigg and Pigglet's General Store}} ({{Pic|24|Oinc}} &times;5) {{Ham|24}}\n|droppedBy = {{Pic|24|Crate}} ({{Pic|24|Hammer}}), {{Pic|20|Slotmachine}} {{SW|24}}<br>\n{{Pic|24|Hot Air Balloon}} ({{Pic|24|Hammer}}) {{Ham|24}}\n}}\n{{Quotes\n|wilson = Soft cloth made from hard roots!\n|willow = Amazing what you can do with bamboo.\n|wolfgang = Flimsy cloth-stuffs.\n|wendy = I wonder if the bamboo finds this new form agreeable?\n|wx78 = PLANT MATTER DERIVATION\n|wickerbottom = A very fine weave.\n|woodie = How do I dye it plaid?\n|maxwell = I've fashioned the bamboo into something useful.\n|wagstaff = Functional and flexible.\n|wigfrid = Sewing is nöt warriör's wörk...\n|webber = We could make a new blankie. Or not.\n|walani = Where did my sticks go? I've been bamboozled!\n|warly = Soft and crisp, all at once.\n|woodlegs = Fabric fer a sail!\n|wilba = 'TIS THE FABRIC OF MINE FOLLY'\n|wormwood = Soft. Made from friends\n|wheeler = The same stuff my balloon is made out of.\n|choose = wilson}}\n'''Cloth''' is a [[Refined]] [[Items|Item]] introduced in the ''[[Shipwrecked]]'' DLC. It requires a [[Science Machine]] to prototype and 3 [[Bamboo]] to craft. Cloth can also be occasionally found when [[Hammer]]ing [[Crate]]s or floating on the water in [[Ocean#Shipwrecked|Ship Graveyards]]. It is used in many crafting recipes and can be used as [[Fuel]].\n\n=={{Pic|32|Hamlet icon}} Hamlet==\nCloth is also included in the ''[[Don't Starve: Hamlet|Hamlet]]'' DLC, required to craft [[Pith Hat]]s and [[Gas Mask]]s. However, it cannot be refined from [[Bamboo]] until the blueprint has been obtained from hammering the [[A Smashing Pot|'A Smashing Pot']] , so players must acquire Cloth through different means. A piece of Cloth can be acquired by hammering the [[Hot Air Balloon|hot air balloon]] debris scattered around the player's spawn point. Cloth can also be bought in the [[Pigg and Pigglet's General Store]] for 5 [[Oinc]]s. \n\nThere is a small chance(around 7%) for Bamboo to be obtained from hammering the [[A Smashing Pot|'A Smashing Pot']] and the corresponding [[blueprint]] for making cloth from it (has 4% chance). Another way for obtaining cloth, is through [[Trawl Net|trawling]] in the hamlet ponds (1.96% chance).\n\n{{clear}}\n=={{Pic|32|Icon Tools}} Usage ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Cloth\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Bamboo\n|count2 = 2\n|item3 = Rope\n|count3 = 2\n|tool = Alchemy Engine\n|result = Cloth Sail\n|dlc = Shipwrecked}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Cloth\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Vine\n|count2 = 2\n|item3 = Empty Bottle\n|count3 = 3\n|tool = Science Machine\n|result = Life Jacket\n|dlc = Shipwrecked}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Cloth\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Sand\n|count2 = 3\n|tool = Science Machine\n|result = Sand Bag\n|resultcount = 4\n|dlc = Shipwrecked}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Cloth\n|item2 = Snakeskin\n|count2 = 2\n|tool = Alchemy Engine\n|result = Snakeskin Rug\n|dlc = Shipwrecked}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Cloth\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Blubber\n|count2 = 4\n|item3 = Palm Leaf\n|count3 = 2\n|tool = Alchemy Engine\n|result = Blubber Suit\n|dlc = Shipwrecked}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Cloth\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Tar\n|count2 = 4\n|item3 = Palm Leaf\n|count3 = 2\n|tool = Science Machine\n|result = Tar Suit\n|dlc = Shipwrecked}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Cloth\n|item2 = Blubber\n|count2 = 2\n|item3 = Rope\n|tool = Alchemy Engine\n|result = Windbreaker\n|dlc = Shipwrecked}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Cloth\n|item2 = Vine\n|count2 = 3\n|item3 = Cork\n|count3 = 6\n|tool = Alchemy Engine\n|result = Pith Hat\n|dlc = Hamlet}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Cloth\n|item2 = Peagawk Plume\n|count2 = 4\n|item3 = Pig Skin\n|tool = Alchemy Engine\n|result = Gas Mask\n|dlc = Hamlet}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Cloth\n|count1 = 3\n|item2 = Bone Shards\n|count2 = 4\n|item3 = Dubloons\n|count3 = 10\n|result = Lucky Hat\n|character = Woodlegs}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Cloth\n|item2 = Rope\n|result = Chef Pouch\n|character = Warly}}\n{{Craftable Items}}\n\n[[es:Tela]]\n[[pl:Tkanina (DSS)]]\n[[vi:Vải]]\n[[Category:Fuel]]\n[[Category:Flammable Objects]]\n[[Category:Refine Tab]]\n[[Category:Hamlet]]"
